com.rds_software.customers.menarini.projects.odp.frontend.forms

Class OdpDetailForm.Setup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rds_software.customers.menarini.projects.odp.frontend.forms.OdpDetailForm.Setup
  • Enclosing class:
    OdpDetailForm

    public static class OdpDetailForm.Setup
extends Object
    Setup configuration for the ODP detail form.

    Determines the form's operating mode (creation or edit) by specifying a company for new ODPs or an existing ODP for editing. The company is always required (extracted from the ODP in edit mode).
